text: Martin Heinze (born 5 January 1939) is a German wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics, the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:German male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the United Team of Germany Category:Olympic wrestlers of East Germany Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics
